(64, 1, '2018-02-22 22:54:52', '2018-02-22 19:54:52', '<div id=\"pl-57\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-57-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">ГАРАНТИЯ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Мы уверены в качестве производимых товаров &#8212; на всю продукцию представляется гарантия.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ></div><div id=\"pgc-57-0-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-0-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">КАЧЕСТВО</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Все нашы товары пройшли сертификацию и полностью отвечают европейським и росийським стандартам качества.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-57-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">СОВМЕСТИМОСТЬ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Авточехлы шьются по заводским лекалам Вашего автомобиля 100% соответствие.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-1-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ></div><div id=\"pgc-57-1-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-1-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">УДОБСТВО В ИСПОЛЬЗОВАНИИ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Используя наши чехлы Вы экономите на химчистке салона. Чехлы легко снимаются и чистятся.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-57-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-57-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"WP_Widget_Media_Image\"]<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"{&quot;instance&quot;:{&quot;attachment_id&quot;:58,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:\\/\\/lviv.loc\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/our-advantages-bg-246x300.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:522,&quot;height&quot;:636,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_type&quot;:&quot;custom&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;image_classes&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_classes&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_rel&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_target_blank&quot;:false,&quot;image_title&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;args&quot;:{&quot;before_widget&quot;:&quot;&lt;div id=\\&quot;panel-57-2-0-0\\&quot; class=\\&quot;so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\\&quot; data-index=\\&quot;4\\&quot; data-style=\\&quot;{&amp;quot;background_display&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;tile&amp;quot;}\\&quot; &gt;&quot;,&quot;after_widget&quot;:&quot;&lt;\\/div&gt;&quot;,&quot;before_title&quot;:&quot;&lt;h3 class=\\&quot;widget-title\\&quot;&gt;&quot;,&quot;after_title&quot;:&quot;&lt;\\/h3&gt;&quot;,&quot;widget_id&quot;:&quot;widget-2-0-0&quot;}}\" />[/siteorigin_widget]</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-57-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">СОБСТВЕНОЕ ПРОИЗВОДСТВО</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Мы располагаем собственным швейным предприятием, а значит готовы учесть все Вашы пожелания при пошыве чехлов.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-3-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ></div><div id=\"pgc-57-3-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-3-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"6\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">СОБЛЮДЕНИЕ СРОКОВ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Мы никогда не заставляем Вас ждать, потому что всегда укладываемся в срок.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-57-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">ВЫГОДНЫЕ ЦЕНЫ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Мы сами являемся производителями, поэтому Вам не придеться иметь дело с посредниками, а соответсвино &#8212; переплачивать.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-4-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-4-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"8\" >			<div class=\"textwidget\"></div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-4-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-4-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"9\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">БЕЗОПАСНОСТЬ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Нашы чехлы обеспечивают не толька Ваш комфорт, красоту салона, но и прежде всего-безопасность. Чехлы сконструированы таким образом, чтобы не препятсвоватьсрабатыванию подушек безопастности.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div></div></div>', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '57-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-22 22:54:52', '2018-02-22 19:54:52'